            <p class="text-lg text-stone-700 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
                The Data Lakehouse is a modern, open architecture that combines the best of both worlds. It implements the reliability and performance of Data Warehouses directly on the low-cost, flexible storage of Data Lakes.
            </p>
            
            <div class="bg-white p-6 md:p-10 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-center mb-8">Data Warehouse + Data Lake = Data Lakehouse</h3>
