            <p class="text-lg text-stone-700 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
                This new architecture is powered by key open technologies that provide reliability and governance directly on your cloud data lake (like Azure ADLS or GCP GCS).
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
