                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-700">Delta Lake</h3>
                    <p class="text-stone-600">
                        An open-source storage layer that brings **ACID transactions**, schema enforcement, and reliability to your Data Lake. It's the "secret sauce" that makes the Lakehouse possible.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
                    <div class="text-5xl mb-4">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-purple-700">Unity Catalog</h3>
                    <p class="text-stone-600">
                        The **unified governance solution** for all data and AI assets. It provides one place to manage permissions, audit access, and discover data, solving the governance challenge.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-center">
                    <div class="text-5xl mb-4">‚òÅÔ∏è</div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-gray-700">Open Cloud Platform</h3>
                    <p class="text-stone-600">
                        The entire Lakehouse runs on your **own cloud storage** (Azure, GCP, AWS). This openness prevents vendor lock-in and gives you full control over your data and costs.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

